    <item>
      <title>英国开始为最强大的模型起草人工智能法规</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/uk-starts-drafting-ai-regulations-for-most-powerful-models</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，英国正在开始起草管理人工智能的法规，重点关注支撑 OpenAI 的 ChatGPT 的最强大的语言模型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/uk-starts-drafting-ai-regulations-for-most-powerful-models</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 15:49:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝恩公司将以 12.5 亿英镑的价格将英国薪资技术公司 Zellis 出售给 Apax</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/bain-to-sell-1-25-billion-uk-payroll-tech-firm-zellis-to-apax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份声明称，贝恩资本已同意将英国薪资软件公司 Zellis Group 出售给 Apax Partners，该公司的客户包括百货公司 Harrods 和汽车制造商 Jaguar。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/bain-to-sell-1-25-billion-uk-payroll-tech-firm-zellis-to-apax</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 15:46:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于分析师对估值和增长前景争论不休，Reddit 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/reddit-shares-slip-as-analysts-debate-valuation-growth-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在众多华尔街分析师开始对该社交媒体公司进行报道后，Reddit Inc. 股价周一下跌 5.1%，触及 3 月份上市以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/reddit-shares-slip-as-analysts-debate-valuation-growth-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 15:37:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国计划与大型科技公司谈判以限制青少年的网络伤害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/uk-plans-talks-with-big-tech-to-limit-online-harm-for-teens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，英国政府计划与 Alphabet Inc.、苹果公司和其他科技巨头进行谈判，推动他们签署一项自愿宪章，赋予父母对青少年使用社交媒体的更多控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/uk-plans-talks-with-big-tech-to-limit-online-harm-for-teens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 14:50:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉高管巴格利诺离职，马斯克失去另一位高级副手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/tesla-executive-baglino-leaves-as-musk-loses-another-top-deputy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司(Tesla Inc.)的两名高管在该汽车制造商有史以来最大规模的一轮裁员中离职，因为电动汽车需求放缓导致该公司将全球员工人数减少了10%以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/tesla-executive-baglino-leaves-as-musk-loses-another-top-deputy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:20:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Clearlake 将 Blackbaud 收购报价提高至 41 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/clearlake-makes-sweetened-4-1-billion-offer-to-buy-blackbaud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Clearlake Capital Group LP 提出了收购 Blackbaud Inc. 的报价，出价为每股 80 美元，大约一年前，该收购案被云软件提供商 Blackbaud Inc. 拒绝。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/clearlake-makes-sweetened-4-1-billion-offer-to-buy-blackbaud</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 10:56:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>施罗德将 Revolut 估值提升 45%，显示金融科技反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/revolut-valuation-raised-by-investor-schroders-as-fintech-fortunes-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Revolut Ltd. 的一位股东认为，该公司的估值比一年前增加了 45%，这表明投资者开始对金融科技行业解冻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/revolut-valuation-raised-by-investor-schroders-as-fintech-fortunes-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:23:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查驳回兴登堡指控后，特米诺斯股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/temenos-says-probe-finds-hindenburg-allegations-were-incorrect</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Temenos AG 表示，一项独立调查发现卖空者兴登堡研究公司对该公司的指控“不准确且具有误导性”，该公司股价自 2008 年以来涨幅最大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/temenos-says-probe-finds-hindenburg-allegations-were-incorrect</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 06:24:48 GMT</pubDate>
